<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>交易计划模板 - YTC Trader</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/modern-premium.css">
</head>
<body style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0a0a0f 0%, #0f172a 50%, #0a0a0f 100%); min-height: 100vh;">
    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #06b6d4 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">交易计划模板</h1>
    </div>
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px;">
        <div style="background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
            <h2>交易计划要素</h2>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2; margin-top: 20px;">
                <li>股票代码和名称</li>
                <li>入场价格和理由</li>
                <li>止损价格和位置</li>
                <li>目标价格和盈亏比</li>
                <li>仓位规模</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
